褒められるのが好きなのですか？
Is it being praised that you love?

409
00:34:29,548 --> 00:34:33,548
なりたい自分を摺り替えても
Even if you substitute the person you want to be

410
00:34:33,548 --> 00:34:37,048
笑顔はいつでも素敵ですか？
Is your smile always wonderful?

411
00:34:37,548 --> 00:34:41,248
始まりだけ 夢見て起きる
Dreaming only of the beginning before waking

412
00:34:41,248 --> 00:34:44,848
その先なら いつか
If it's what lies beyond, then someday

413
00:34:44,848 --> 00:34:48,548
自分の腕で
with my own arms

414
00:34:48,548 --> 00:34:52,548
そうだ 大事なものはいつでも
That's right, the important things are always

415
00:34:52,548 --> 00:34:56,548
形のないものだけ
only those that have no form

416
00:34:56,548 --> 00:35:00,048
手に入れようとして 壊していた
I broke them while trying to obtain them

417
00:35:00,056 --> 00:35:01,456
形のないものだけ
Only the things with no shape,

418
00:35:01,456 --> 00:35:03,056
手に入れても なくしても
whether I obtain them or lose them,

419
00:35:03,056 --> 00:35:06,256
気づかぬまま
I remain unaware.

420
00:35:06,356 --> 00:35:07,856
そうさ
That's right,

421
00:35:07,856 --> 00:35:10,556
悲しみを優しさに
turn sadness into kindness,

422
00:35:10,556 --> 00:35:13,556
自分らしさを力に
and your uniqueness into strength.

423
00:35:13,556 --> 00:35:16,856
迷いながらでもいい
It's okay to be lost,

424
00:35:16,856 --> 00:35:21,556
歩き出して
just start walking.

425
00:35:22,856 --> 00:35:24,056
もう一回
One more time!

426
00:35:24,456 --> 00:35:25,856
もう一回
One more time!

427
00:35:26,556 --> 00:35:27,856
もう一回
One more time!

428
00:35:28,356 --> 00:35:29,856
もう一回
One more time!

429
00:40:00,064 --> 00:40:01,364
ように
...so it won't fade away.

430
00:42:44,264 --> 00:42:47,364
Why does everything feel so real?

431
00:42:48,064 --> 00:42:49,464
Am I real?

432
00:42:50,064 --> 00:42:52,264
Can you even feel my existence?

433
00:42:54,464 --> 00:42:57,464
Is this what Deja vu looks like?

434
00:45:43,072 --> 00:45:51,572
All these memories mean the world to me.

435
00:45:53,072 --> 00:46:01,072
Thank you for walking this journey with me.

436
